  "source": {
    "on": "",
    "ru": "Древнеисландский текст: Andreas Heusler, Wilhelm Ranisch: Eddica minora (Dortmund 1903), pp. 53–54, Guðni Jónsson, 1954. Перевод: И. Г. Матюшина. Самые забавные лживые саги: Cборник статей в честь Г. В. Глазыриной. — М.: Русский Фонд Содействия Образованию и Науке, 2012,",
    "en": "An ancient Icelandic text, edited by Finnur Jónsson, Fagrskinna, 1902–1903, pp. 28–30. Translation by Lee M. Hollander (1936)."
  },
  "texts": {
    "on": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "1.",
        "lines": [
          "Mjök er vandgætt,",
          "hvé verða skal",
          "of borinn öðrum",
          "at banorði.",
          "Þik Drótt of bar",
          "af Danmörku,",
          "en mik sjálfan",
          "á Svíþjóðu."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "2.",
        "lines": [
          "Tveir váru þeir",
          "tyrvir gjarnir",
          "Buðla nautar,",
          "nú er brotinn annarr.",
          "Svá höfðu dvergar",
          "dauðir smíðat",
          "sem engi mun",
          "áðr né síðan."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "3.",
        "lines": [
          "Stendr mér at höfði",
          "hlíf in brotna,",
          ".........",
          "eru þar taldir",
          "tigar ins átta",
          "manna þeira,",
          "er ek at morði varð."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "Liggr þar inn svási",
          "sonr at höfði,",
          "eptirerfingi,",
          "er ek eiga gat,",
          ".........",
          "óviljandi",
          "aldrs synjaðak."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "Bið ek þik, bróðir,",
          "bænar einnar,",
          "einnar bænar,",
          "eigi þú synja!",
          "Mik skaltu verja",
          "váðum þínum,",
          "sem fjörs bani",
          "fár annars mun."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "6.",
        "lines": [
          ".........",
          "Nú verð ek liggja",
          "lífs andvana,",
          "mæki undaðr,",
          "þeims magnar sár."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "7",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "",
        "lines": [
          ""
        ],
        "placeholder": true
      },
      {
        "id": "8",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "",
        "lines": [
          ""
        ],
        "placeholder": true
      }
    ],
    "ru": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "1.",
        "lines": [
          "Нелегко предвидеть,",
          "Что может выйти,",
          "Коли один другому",
          "Рожден на погибель.",
          "Дротт из Дании",
          "Тебя родила,",
          "Меня же самого —",
          "В земле свейской."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "2.",
        "lines": [
          "Два было их",
          "Рьяных меча,",
          "Подарка Будли",
          "Теперь один разбит.",
          "Дверги так их",
          "Сковали мёртвые,",
          "Как никто не смог бы",
          "Ни прежде, ни впредь."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "3.",
        "lines": [
          "Стоит у меня в головах",
          "Щит расколотый,",
          ",,,,,,,,,",
          "На нём посчитаны",
          "Восемь десятков",
          "Воинов тех,",
          "Что мною убиты."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "Лежит там милый",
          "Сын во главе,",
          "Наследник мой,",
          "Мною рожденный,",
          ".........",
          "Не желая того,",
          "Его жизни лишил я."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "Я прошу тебя, брат,",
          "Об одном одолжении,",
          "Всего об одном,",
          "Не откажи!",
          "Оберни ты меня",
          "В одежды свои,",
          "Как забравший жизнь",
          "Для другого не сделает."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "6.",
        "lines": [
          ".........",
          "Теперь должен я лежать",
          "Лишённый жизни,",
          "Раненный мечом,",
          "Который множит раны."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "7",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "",
        "lines": [
          ""
        ],
        "placeholder": true
      },
      {
        "id": "8",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "",
        "lines": [
          ""
        ],
        "placeholder": true
      }
    ],
    "en": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "1.",
        "lines": [
          "(“ Tis time to tell, on turf as I lie,",
          "felled by the sword, what fate was ours:",
          "unlike our lot in life hath been,",
          "to Hel fare I while whole thou livest.)"
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "2.",
        "lines": [
          "Not easy is it ever to know",
          "who will be born his brother’s slayer.",
          "Did Drótt bear thee in Danish lands;",
          "myself she bore in Sweden’s realm."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "3.",
        "lines": [
          "(“By the same mother suckled we were;",
          "yet neither the other knew as brother",
          "until the twain, trusting their weapon,",
          "for the fray eager, fought the other:)"
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "4",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "4.",
        "lines": [
          "Trusty broad-swords twain were forged—",
          "heirlooms from Buthli; now one is broken.",
          "So deftly had the dwarfs forged them",
          "as none e’er did or will do, hereafter."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "5",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "5.",
        "lines": [
          "By my head, broken, my buckler stands,",
          "(round-shaped, shining, but shattered now;)",
          "on it are scored eighty notches",
          "for doughty men given to death by me."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "6",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "6.",
        "lines": [
          "My liefest son lies by my head,",
          "the after-heir whom I did have—",
          "* * *",
          "unwittingly in war I slew him."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "7",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "7.",
        "lines": [
          "One boon, brother, I beg of thee—",
          "one boon only albeit one",
          "which slayer not often to slain man grants:",
          "in thy weeds of war wind my body!"
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      },
      {
        "id": "8",
        "type": "stanza",
        "number": "8.",
        "lines": [
          "(Have hateful norns knit our fate-thread:",
          "to fight against fate the fey one avails not:)",
          "lifeless shall I now lie on the ground,",
          "slain by the sword, sorely wounded."
        ],
        "placeholder": false
      }
    ]
  }
}